object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT
            lkp_policy_key.policy_key
            FROM dbo.import_homeowners_rating_17
            LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.lkp_policy_key
                ON import_homeowners_rating_17.policy_number = lkp_policy_key.policy_number AND import_homeowners_rating_17.policy_symbol = lkp_policy_key.policy_symbol AND import_homeowners_rating_17.module_number = lkp_policy_key.module_number AND import_homeowners_rating_17.company_number = lkp_policy_key.company_number
        UNION
        SELECT DISTINCT
            lkp_policy_key.policy_key
            FROM dbo.import_fire_rating_14
            LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.lkp_policy_key
                ON import_fire_rating_14.policy_number = lkp_policy_key.policy_number AND import_fire_rating_14.policy_symbol = lkp_policy_key.policy_symbol AND import_fire_rating_14.module_number = lkp_policy_key.module_number AND import_fire_rating_14.company_number = lkp_policy_key.company_number
        UNION
        SELECT DISTINCT
            lkp_policy_key.policy_key
            FROM dbo.import_bop_rating_10
            LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.lkp_policy_key
                ON import_bop_rating_10.policy_number = lkp_policy_key.policy_number AND import_bop_rating_10.policy_symbol = lkp_policy_key.policy_symbol AND import_bop_rating_10.module_number = lkp_policy_key.module_number AND import_bop_rating_10.company_number = lkp_policy_key.company_number
